    "long_instructions": "### **Analyzing Layered Defenses**\r\n\r\n#### **Instructions:**  \r\n\r\n1. **Click the link** below in order to create a copy of the activity guide\r\n\r\n2. **Explore** the user interactivity of one of the four apps presented on Level 2.\r\n\r\n3. **Drag and Drop the colored dots and the comment boxes** onto app diagrams within your activity guide to annotate potential vulnerabilities.\r\n\r\n4. Use the **Layered Defense Menu resource** to plan security upgrades for the vulnerabilities that you highlighted.\r\n\r\n\r\n",
